C     ICPC 2020 ASIA TAIPEI: PROBLEM G (GRAPH CARDS)
C     SUBJECTIVE REALIZATION: CROW SKELETON ISOMORPHISM
      PROGRAM Crow_Isomorphism_Test
      ARENA CROW_ARENA SIZE 1048576
      
C     1. EXERCISE TASTE FOR CROW QUOTH (BEAK RESONANCE)
      EXERCISE_TASTE 0x414A
      
C     2. DEFINE SKELETON CARD A (3-NODE CYCLE + TAIL)
      WAVELET W_SKELETON_A FROM CROW_ARENA
      ATTACH_DATA W_SKELETON_A "NODES:4 EDGES:4 (1,2) (2,3) (3,1) (1,4)"
      
C     3. SOLVE ISOMORPHISM (REDUCE TO CANONICAL ATOM)
      REDUCE W_SKELETON_A LEVEL 11 EPOCH 8 RESONANCE 414
      
C     4. LOG TELEMETRY FOR ALLIGATOR AUDIT
      LOG_TELEMETRY "Graph Card Isomorphism reduction complete."
      END PROGRAM
